  "texts": [
    "In Abuzayed and Al-Khalifa (2021), several BERT models were utilized, and the DA process was applied to tweets to enhance the performance of sentiment detection.",
    "Another study (Alkadri 2022) investigated the effect of using DA for Arabic tweets in the spam detection task.",
    "Their focus was on addressing the dataset imbalance problem by increasing the instances of minority classes.",
    "They utilized a large corpus to extract Word2Vec embedding vectors to represent tweet contents.",
    "A notable exploration into DL methodologies was conducted by Ajao et al. (2018), employing recurrent neural networks (RNN) and long short-term memory models (LSTM) for social media text classification."
  ],
